text: Galina Sidorova (born 6 March 1945) is a Soviet alpine skier. She competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics and the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
